<normalizedToken originalValue="B–D">B-D</normalizedToken>
Shells, USNM 1004185, USNM 905091, USNM 1004183 E, F Opercula (outer, inner sides), USNM 847246 G Portion of radular ribbon, USNM 847246 H Central teeth, USNM 847246 I Lateral and inner marginal teeth, USNM 847246. Scale bars 
